{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01K8NZS6NZW3EYNKYGY9HgBC","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→---\n     2→name: entity-skill\n     3→description: \"JPA Entity + Repository 작성 가이드\"\n     4→---\n     5→\n     6→# Entity Skill\n     7→\n     8→## 설명\n     9→\n    10→새로운 JPA Entity와 Repository를 프로젝트 컨벤션에 맞게 작성한다.\n    11→\n    12→## 실행 절차\n    13→\n    14→### 1. Entity 작성\n    15→\n    16→위치: `domain/src/main/kotlin/com/maum/backend/entity/{도메인}/`\n    17→\n    18→```kotlin\n    19→@Entity\n    20→@Table(catalog = \"{catalog}\", name = \"{table_name}\")\n    21→class EntityName(\n    22→    @Id\n    23→    @GeneratedValue(generator = \"uuid2\")\n    24→    @GenericGenerator(name = \"uuid2\", strategy = \"uuid2\")\n    25→    val id: String = \"\",\n    26→\n    27→    // 비즈니스 필드\n    28→    val userId: String,\n    29→    val name: String,\n    30→\n    31→    // 관계 매핑 (필요시)\n    32→    @ManyToOne(fetch = FetchType.LAZY)\n    33→    @JoinColumn(name = \"category_id\", referencedColumnName = \"code\")\n    34→    val category: CategoryEntity? = null,\n    35→\n    36→    // 감사 필드\n    37→    @CreatedDate\n    38→    @Column(columnDefinition = \"datetime(3)\", nullable = false, updatable = false)\n    39→    var createdAt: LocalDateTime = LocalDateTime.now(),\n    40→\n    41→    @LastModifiedDate\n    42→    var updatedAt: LocalDateTime = LocalDateTime.now(),\n    43→)\n    44→```\n    45→\n    46→### 2. Repository 작성\n    47→\n    48→위치: `domain/src/main/kotlin/com/maum/backend/repository/{도메인}/`\n    49→\n    50→```kotlin\n    51→interface EntityNameRepository : JpaRepository<EntityName, String> {\n    52→    fun findByUserId(userId: String): List<EntityName>\n    53→    fun findByUserIdAndStatus(userId: String, status: Int): List<EntityName>\n    54→}\n    55→```\n    56→\n    57→### 3. Catalog 선택\n    58→\n    59→| Catalog | 도메인 |\n    60→|---------|--------|\n    61→| `maum` | user, profile, call, product, follow |\n    62→| `moment` | post, moment, comment, like |\n    63→| `chat` | chat_room |\n    64→| `notification` | notification, notification_setting |\n    65→\n    66→### 4. 컴파일 확인\n    67→\n    68→```bash\n    69→./gradlew :domain:compileKotlin\n    70→```\n    71→\n    72→## 주의사항\n    73→\n    74→- Entity는 `var` 최소화, 변경 필요한 필드만 `var`\n    75→- `@Table`의 `catalog`는 실제 DB 카탈로그명과 일치\n    76→- `@JoinColumn`의 `referencedColumnName`을 명시적으로 지정 (기본값 `id`가 아닌 경우)\n    77→- 양방향 관계보다 단방향 관계 우선\n    78→\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01B6YcBo599K6WKEN9QNNvjB","session_id":"50a4c89a-d59b-4872-adf3-d2353d38eca5","uuid":"dbf17047-8c95-45ce-9c7f-26dfabf6d072"}
